node.text:
I am opening 4 commission slots ♥️

STATUS: all slots taken. Thank you! 

Please help share this post, so I find client who may be interested. I posted my commission info in my IG story through link. 

❗️Please reach out only through email. If you DM me, there’s a slim chance I’ll see your message because my DM is over-flooded. ❗️

This is not first come first serve, I’ll be looking at the details you provided in your email to see if I am capable of doing it or not. Thank you ~

#semirealism #digitalpainting #artwork #drawing #illustration #portrait
